{"tid":278371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本愛知縣高速公路旅巴與私家車相撞 　1死20傷","createTime":"2017-06-10T11:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T16:56:41.000Z","uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8eba9f2baaf2dfa2b4c5b54e36783fea42b91d8d","tid":278371,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"日本愛知縣東名高速公路發生旅遊巴與私家車相撞意外，造成至少1死20人受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n意外發生在當地時間今早7時多，肇事旅遊巴在東名高速公路上行駛時，輛一私家車逆線撞向旅巴，由於衝力剷向旅巴車頂，旅遊巴車頭嚴重損毀，玻璃窗碎片和零件已散落在路上，警方及8輛消防車趕到現場，封鎖現場交通拯救傷者，令公路大排長龍。私家車司機當場死亡<br />\n<br />\n警方說，旅遊巴上有大約40名乘客，至少1死20人受傷送院。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DB8H47dVoAAtmLp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDB8H47dVoAAtmLp.jpg&h=aa26e4c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DB8H5cSUAAE4aak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDB8H5cSUAAE4aak.jpg&h=fa15f94f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DB7wDsiUIAAeIBb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDB7wDsiUIAAeIBb.jpg&h=b5c5d761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DB7vpOBVoAAVvNi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDB7vpOBVoAAVvNi.jpg&h=4c91b5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DB7vpOBUwAExVEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDB7vpOBUwAExVEL.jpg&h=a375934e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29d52e07566a5c556ae08acd1171a4d2b53e02b1","tid":278371,"uid":52520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"究竟點撞先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9673905d9bbfb2e6da773eaece01dc198dd82358","tid":278371,"uid":77134,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:28:05.000Z",